# P2P Chat Demo Script for Console
# This demonstrates the ICQ-style chat interface

# Set username first
`username Alice`

# Create a channel
`publish dev-chat`

# Send some messages
"Welcome to the dev-chat channel!"
"This is a P2P chat system using RakNet"

# Check who's in the channel
`users`

# Discover available channels
`discover`

# Example of leaving and joining
`leave`
`discover`
`enter dev-chat`

# Send another message
"I'm back in the channel!"

# Get help
`help`